description: I´ve always liked football. At one point in my life, I was even considering a football player career. That´s why I was very excited when I met a guy who was on the way to a local football field. A group of friends decided to have a nice afternoon match. I was told that only boys would be there, which made me even more excited. And it was amazing, it was almost impossible to choose from all those cuties. Eventually I found two that were willing to talk and even to show some skin. The field was just next to a street so we couldn´t do more than showing dicks. Fortunately, the boys knew the area well and took me to a nearby forest where we had all the privacy we needed. There I put their friendship on a whole new level.
title: Czech Hunter 314
